<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redirect Example</title>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Your iframe -->
    <iframe id="myIframe" src="https://example.com"></iframe>

    <script>
        // Function to redirect the parent page
        function redirectToNewPage() {
            // Access the parent window (top level)
            const parentWindow = window.parent;
            
            // Change the location of the parent window
            parentWindow.location.href = 'https://newpage.com';
        }

        // Example: Redirect after a button click
        const redirectButton = document.createElement('button');
        redirectButton.textContent = 'Redirect';
        redirectButton.addEventListener('click', redirectToNewPage);
        document.body.appendChild(redirectButton);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
